    "attributes": {
        "action": "Tell schools to take sickness into account for attendance awards",
        "additional_details": "I think we should still have rewards but it would not count on their attendance if they have any kind of an appointment (with proof) or is sick. The Government\u2019s guidance should say this.",
        "background": "Children with constant hospital appointments never get attendance awards. It\u2019s not fair if others have fun and they don\u2019t just because they have a medical condition.",
